---
title: Moroccan-Style Pork & Roast Veggie Couscous with Herby Yoghurt & Walnuts
description: Quality protein and a roasted veggie couscous are the base of this Moroccan-inspired dish. Just add a hit of herby yoghurt and crunchy walnuts to tie all the nutritionally balanced elements together!
